es.uca.spifm.spdt.genericTools.itm

Interface Issue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IssueImpl

    public interface Issue
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Issue'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Description
    • Done Ratio
    • Estimated Hours
    • Elapsed Hours
    • Tracker
    • Status
    • Dependencies
    • Category
    • Priority
    • Due Date
    • Completed Date

    See Also:
    ItmPackage.getIssue()
